{"tid":2352174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國新修訂的國防法1月1日生效新增四個字引發關注","createTime":"2021-01-03T23:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T01:45:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83c3644db12f7fbcdaeac8724acb6f406714bd7c","tid":2352174,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T23:11:16.000Z","msg":"中國新修訂的國防法1月1日生效新增四個字引發關注<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-new-defense-law-expands-power-of-its-military/5722900.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fchina-new-defense-law-expands-power-of-its-military%2F5722900.html&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=41d9a01a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/china-new-defense-law-expands-power-of-its-military/5722900.html</a><br />\n<br />\n華盛頓&mdash; <br />\n中國經過修改的《國防法》1月1日正式生效。新修訂的中國國防法首次將&ldquo;分裂&rdquo;和保護&ldquo;發展利益&rdquo;作為動員、部署軍隊和預備役部隊的理由添加到立法中。其中&ldquo;發展利益&rdquo;這四個字在新修訂的國防法中頻繁出現，引起外界關注。<br />\n<br />\n有觀察人士注意到，&ldquo;發展利益&rdquo;四個字在這部新修訂的法律中一共出現四次，反應出中國國防張力的擴充，以及對外戰略姿態的巨大轉變。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;發展利益&rdquo;在該法中第一次出現是在總則第二條，即&ldquo;國家為防備和抵抗侵略，制止武裝顛覆和分裂，保衛國家主權、統一、領土完整、安全和發展利益所進行的軍事活動，以及與軍事有關的政治、經濟、外交、科技、教育等方面的活動，適用本法&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n該條款中提到的國家主權等內容都屬於中國的國家核心利益範疇。&ldquo;中國核心利益&rdquo;包括：國家主權，國家安全，領土完整，國家統一等。習近平說過，&ldquo;任何外國不要指望我們會拿自己的核心利益做交易，不要指望我們會吞下損害我國主權、安全、發展利益的苦果&rdquo; 。<br />\n<br />\n分析人士認為，中國通過修訂國防法擴大習近平領導的軍隊的權利。這也就意味著，如果中國的&ldquo;發展利益&rdquo;受到威脅，將可能主動發起戰爭。中國將可能展現出更多的戰爭主動性。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防法修正案經過兩年的審議，於2020年12月26日由中國的全國人大會議通過。"},{"pid":"1d70c585bfa4dbe007b6d16c8d3be17c7be6639a","tid":2352174,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T23:15:53.000Z","msg":"發展利益 = 習近平嘅利益<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O5R0qN8ZwCE/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FO5R0qN8ZwCE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d6147b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jhH4yZ9GfOM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjhH4yZ9GfOM%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=10a7b9e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"610051bccd8425359072cb8faf03b966dc45eb46","tid":2352174,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T23:23:55.000Z","msg":"用韭菜發電打杖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e899e8a2ab88154b3ee59d9540f4f082acc43357","tid":2352174,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"用石頭發電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ebd50a6f520e4993859114b886813346b51c04","tid":2352174,"uid":224106,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T23:40:38.000Z","msg":"日本二戰都因為發展利益受阻<br />\n發動珍珠港事變"},{"pid":"c25f18db805f5e955a21afc6f5590419045fadbd","tid":2352174,"uid":163801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"即係任何公司同國企競爭就中招喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333a22cb0c640e7596bb460545136188a9905e23","tid":2352174,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"海參威"},{"pid":"216a5f33192472802e86964e153c67fa60e070d2","tid":2352174,"uid":293947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"制裁中國就要開戰"},{"pid":"bf5279bba11979b6d0ccfbd9f6354880105f7bcf","tid":2352174,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c25f18db805f5e955a21afc6f5590419045fadbd","tid":2352174,"uid":163801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"即係任何公司同國企競爭就中招喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:44:57.000Z","msg":"馬雲"},{"pid":"6ba835aa0daa8acfcbdfba8446545a3366ba8bc9","tid":2352174,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89ebd50a6f520e4993859114b886813346b51c04","tid":2352174,"uid":224106,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T23:40:38.000Z","msg":"日本二戰都因為發展利益受阻<br />\n發動珍珠港事變"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T01:45:54.000Z","msg":"美國佬4年收日本皮"}]}